<td class="postcell">
<div>
    <div class="post-text" itemprop="description">
        <p>I need to hash some passwords with salt on postgresql, and I haven't been able to find any relevant documentation on how to get that done.  </p>

<p>So how can I hash passwords (with some salts) in postgresql?</p>

